<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3145382" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="1"><link href="text/shared/optionen/01060400.xhp" name="Sort Lists">Sort Lists</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3153825" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><ahelp hid="HID_SCPAGE_USERLISTS">All user-defined lists are displayed in the<emph> Sort Lists </emph>dialog. You can also define and edit your own lists. Only text can be used as sort lists, no numbers.</ahelp><comment>UFI: fix to #111848#</comment></paragraph>
</section>
